        <div class="project static-stack">
            <h2>Static Stack Implementation</h2>
            <img src="blackjack.jpg" alt="Blackjack picture">
            <p>In this project, I implemented a static stack data structure and used it in a simple Blackjack game. I included two Word documents: "Specifikacio," which documents essential information about the stack data structure, and "Blackjack," which contains the game's statement. Both documents are in Hungarian.</p>
